    "story_name": "法尔艾斯 第5话 自由如风",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我本应在那天死去。\\n我曾诅咒这命运的不公。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "为什么只有我要被迫承受\\n这种没有自由的人生？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "于是我向命运抗争，\\n不惜染指禁忌\\n并复活“起始之人”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "啊，我至死都是个自私的罪人。\\n明明给这个世界带来了灾难，\\n却在这最后一刻感到了幸福。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "能与我的兄弟再次像这样交谈，\\n让我再次感觉自己\\n身为“法尔艾斯”十分幸福。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "所以，这次我会接受自己的死亡。\\n因为我本就不该活到今天。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "而且如果能用我的性命\\n保护我重要的兄弟，\\n那我无怨无悔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "开什么玩笑！\\n你不是比任何人都希望\\n自己能活着吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "莱昂……尼多？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你这蠢货终于醒了，\\n什么“无怨无悔”……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你不是因为无论如何都想要活下去，\\n才会染指禁忌的吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "那你又怎能轻易接受死亡！\\n不到最后一刻都不准给我放弃挣扎！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "请您好好倾听一下\\n自己的心声吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你真的是甘心\\n接受死亡吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "（不……\\n不是那样的……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "（我唯一的愿望就是——）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我要活下去……\\n我还……不想死！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "那就不要放弃，\\n反抗你的命运。\\n像你这样等死有什么意义。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "呵呵……你说得……没错……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "啧……那家伙也已经恢复力量了吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "莱昂尼多……\\n把乌拉诺斯引到我这边来……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你是要当诱饵吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "嗯……我会在乌拉诺斯袭向\\n我的瞬间吸取他体内残存的魔力。\\n你则趁机杀掉他……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "相信我，\\n我还不打算死在这一战……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "好吧……\\n我们上，玛斯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "这边！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "乌拉诺斯……\\n这黑暗魔力因我而起，\\n如今就由我亲手让你解脱……哈啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "趁现在！莱昂尼多！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "这次一定会让你解脱的！\\n哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……\\n这下总算结束了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "多谢了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "能帮上你的忙就好……\\n咳咳！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你这人还真是不会撒谎。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你在说些什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "刚才是谁说\\n不打算死在这里的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我可没有骗你……\\n我没有死于刚才那一战……不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你这身体……已经到极限了吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我没有遗憾……\\n这一刻……我终于能够凭自己的意志\\n选择自己的人生……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "啊……不过……\\n果然我还是不想死啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "如果可以的话……我希望……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "法尔艾斯……\\n嗯？这魔力的气息是！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这里是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "久违了，吾之契约者。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "乌拉诺斯！？\\n你怎么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "如今正是吾向你报恩的时候。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "报恩？\\n你难道是指……\\n当年我救你一命那事？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我没有资格让你报恩，\\n毕竟我把你当做了实验品。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "那又如何？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "倘若没能遇到你，\\n吾早在那天便已经死去。\\n更不可能有机会成为你的实验品。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "难道……你是自愿……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "吾在漫长的岁月中积累了不少知识。\\n但人类却总是能够不断地创造新的事物，\\n远远超越吾的智慧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "所以吾十分好奇，得到吾的知识\\n的人类究竟会有怎样的成果。\\n那真是一段愉快的时光。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "原来我们是一丘之貉啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "没错。\\n所以吾才会与仍是孩子的你缔结契约。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "名为契约的联系十分有用。\\n即使吾濒临死亡，\\n也还是成功地将魔力注入到了你的体内。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "难道……我体内的那魔力是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "法尔艾斯，活下去吧。\\n用你这条命，\\n自由地见证人类的智慧吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "吾即使失去了肉体，\\n也会化作你的魔力，\\n与你一同见证人类的进化。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "乌拉诺斯……乌拉诺斯，\\n等等！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "乌拉诺斯",
            "context": "你给吾带来了乐趣，\\n这就当做是对你的饯别礼了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "乌拉诺斯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "……\\n这里是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你终于醒了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "谢斯？\\n我还活着吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我可没有什么\\n能与死人说话的能力哦？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "莱昂尼多……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "乌拉诺斯的魔力覆盖你的全身之后，\\n你的伤就好了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "真是让人吃惊呢。\\n我都带着医疗部队来了，\\n却几乎没派上什么用场。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "别说是战斗中受的伤，\\n就连你原本坏死的肉体也恢复了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你身为“起始之人”的傀儡\\n所留下的后遗症也几乎都消失了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "是吗……\\n是乌拉诺斯救了我啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "（我体内这未知的魔力\\n来自于乌拉诺斯……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "（原本早该坏死的身体\\n之所以能撑到现在，\\n原来也是因为他的魔力啊。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
